<div class="tab followers" data-group="primary" data-tab="followers">
<div class="stonetop-followers">

	{{!-- ── Animal Companion (Ranger) ──────────────────────────── --}}
	{{#if stonetop.followers.animalCompanion}}
	{{#with stonetop.followers.animalCompanion}}
	<div class="stonetop-follower-card">
		<div class="stonetop-follower-header">
			<div class="stonetop-follower-title">
				<span class="stonetop-follower-name">
					{{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}Animal Companion{{/if}}{{#if pronoun}} <span class="stonetop-follower-pronoun">({{pronoun}})</span>{{/if}}
					{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}<input class="stonetop-animal-companion-pronoun-input stonetop-follower-pronoun-input" type="text" value="{{pronoun}}" placeholder="pronoun…" maxlength="10">{{/if}}
				</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-type">{{#if kind}}{{kindDisplay}} ({{typeDisplay}}){{else}}{{type}}{{/if}}</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-stats">
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat">
					<strong>HP</strong>
					<span class="stonetop-follower-hp-track">
						<input class="stonetop-follower-hp-input" type="number"
						       data-follower="animal-companion"
						       value="{{hpCurrent}}" min="0" max="{{hpMax}}">
						<span class="stonetop-hp-sep">/</span>
						<span class="stonetop-hp-max">{{hpMax}}</span>
					</span>
				</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Armor</strong> {{armor}}</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Damage</strong> {{#if damageRoll}}<a class="rollable stonetop-follower-damage-roll" data-roll="{{damageRoll}}" data-follower-type="animal" data-follower-kind="{{#if kind}}{{kind}}{{else}}{{typeDisplay}}{{/if}}" data-follower-name="{{name}}" data-follower-pronoun="{{pronoun}}" data-damage-form="{{damageForm}}"><i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i></a>{{/if}} {{damage}}</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{#if traits.length}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Traits</span>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-tags">
				{{#each traits}}
				<span class="stonetop-follower-tag{{#if tooltip}} stonetop-follower-tag--tooltip{{/if}}"
				      {{#if tooltip}}data-tooltip="{{tooltip}}" data-tooltip-direction="UP"{{/if}}>{{label}}</span>
				{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if instinct}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Instinct</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{instinct}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if cost}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Cost</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{cost}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row stonetop-follower-loyalty-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Loyalty</span>
			<div class="stonetop-loyalty-pips">
				{{#each loyalty}}
				{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
				<button type="button"
				        class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-animal-companion-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"
				        data-index="{{index}}"></button>
				{{else}}
				<span class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-animal-companion-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"></span>
				{{/if}}
				{{/each}}
			</div>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-loyalty">○○○</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	{{/with}}
	{{/if}}

	{{!-- ── Crew (Marshal) ────────────────────────────────────── --}}
	{{#if stonetop.followers.crew}}
	{{#with stonetop.followers.crew}}
	<div class="stonetop-follower-card stonetop-follower-card--crew">
		{{!-- Header --}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-header">
			<div class="stonetop-follower-title">
				{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
				<input class="stonetop-crew-name-input stonetop-follower-name-input"
				       type="text" value="{{name}}" placeholder="Name your crew…">
				{{else}}
				<span class="stonetop-follower-name">{{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}Your Crew{{/if}}</span>
				{{/if}}
				<span class="stonetop-follower-type">group follower</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-stats">
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>HP</strong> 6 each</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Armor</strong> 0</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Damage</strong> <a class="rollable stonetop-follower-damage-roll" data-roll="d6" data-follower-type="crew" data-follower-name="{{name}}" data-follower-pronoun="they" data-damage-form=""><i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i></a> d6</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		{{!-- Tags --}}
		{{#if tags.length}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Tags</span>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-tags">
				{{#each tags}}<span class="stonetop-follower-tag">{{this}}</span>{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/if}}

		{{!-- Instinct / Cost --}}
		{{#if instinct}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Instinct</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{instinct}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if cost}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Cost</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{cost}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}

		{{!-- Loyalty --}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row stonetop-follower-loyalty-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Loyalty</span>
			<div class="stonetop-loyalty-pips">
				{{#each loyalty}}
				{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
				<button type="button"
				        class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-crew-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"
				        data-index="{{index}}"></button>
				{{else}}
				<span class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-crew-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"></span>
				{{/if}}
				{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>

		{{!-- Inventory --}}
		{{#if gear.length}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-section">
			<p class="stonetop-follower-section-heading">Inventory <span class="stonetop-follower-section-subtitle">3 ✓ or fewer is a light load; 4–6 ✓ is a normal load; 7–9 ✓ is a heavy load.</span></p>
			<div class="stonetop-crew-gear-list">
				{{#each gear}}
				<label class="stonetop-crew-gear-item{{#if checked}} is-checked{{/if}}">
					<span class="stonetop-crew-gear-pips">
						{{#each pips}}<input type="checkbox"
						       class="stonetop-crew-gear-check stonetop-crew-pip"
						       data-slug="{{../slug}}" data-pip="{{index}}"
						       {{#if filled}}checked{{/if}}
						       {{#unless @root.stonetop.editMode}}disabled{{/unless}}>{{/each}}
					</span>
					<span>{{{label}}}</span>
				</label>
				{{/each}}
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-crew-supplies-section">
				<p class="stonetop-follower-section-heading">Supplies</p>
				<div class="stonetop-crew-supplies-grid">
					{{#each supplySets}}
					<div class="stonetop-crew-supply-set">
						{{#each pips}}<input type="checkbox"
						       class="stonetop-crew-supplies-pip stonetop-crew-pip"
						       data-set="{{setIndex}}" data-pip="{{pipIndex}}"
						       {{#if filled}}checked{{/if}}
						       {{#unless @root.stonetop.editMode}}disabled{{/unless}}>{{/each}}
					</div>
					{{/each}}
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/if}}

		{{!-- Individuals --}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-section">
			<p class="stonetop-follower-section-heading">Individuals</p>
			{{#if individuals.length}}
			<div class="stonetop-crew-individuals">
				{{#each individuals}}
				<div class="stonetop-crew-individual">
					<div class="stonetop-crew-individual-header">
						<span class="stonetop-crew-individual-name">{{name}}</span>
						<span class="stonetop-follower-hp-track stonetop-follower-hp-track--individual">
							<strong class="stonetop-follower-hp-label">HP</strong>
							<input class="stonetop-follower-hp-input" type="number"
							       data-follower="crew-individual" data-index="{{index}}"
							       value="{{hpCurrent}}" min="0" max="6">
							<span class="stonetop-hp-sep">/</span>
							<span class="stonetop-hp-max">6</span>
						</span>
						{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
						<button type="button" class="stonetop-crew-delete-individual stonetop-inline-btn stonetop-inline-btn--danger"
						        data-index="{{index}}" title="Remove">
							<i class="fas fa-times"></i>
						</button>
						{{/if}}
					</div>
					{{#if tag}}
					<div class="stonetop-crew-individual-row">
						<span class="stonetop-crew-individual-row-label">Tag</span>
						<span class="stonetop-follower-tag">{{tag}}</span>
					</div>
					{{/if}}
					{{#if traits.length}}
					<div class="stonetop-crew-individual-row">
						<span class="stonetop-crew-individual-row-label">Traits</span>
						<div class="stonetop-follower-tags">
							{{#each traits}}<span class="stonetop-follower-tag stonetop-follower-tag--trait">{{this}}</span>{{/each}}
						</div>
					</div>
					{{/if}}
				</div>
				{{/each}}
			</div>
			{{else}}
			<p class="stonetop-follower-empty-note">No notable individuals yet. When one stands out, add them here.</p>
			{{/if}}
			{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
			<button type="button" class="stonetop-crew-create-individual stonetop-inline-btn stonetop-create-individual-btn">
				<i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Create Individual
			</button>
			{{/if}}
		</div>
		{{!-- Group Fight --}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-section stonetop-group-fight-section">
			<p class="stonetop-follower-section-heading">Group Fight
				<span class="stonetop-follower-section-subtitle">treat the whole group as one combatant</span>
			</p>
			<div class="stonetop-group-fight-stats-row">
				<span class="stonetop-group-fight-stat">
					<strong>Group HP</strong>
					{{#if individuals.length}}{{groupHp}}{{else}}—{{/if}}
				</span>
				<span class="stonetop-group-fight-stat"><strong>Armor</strong> 0</span>
				<span class="stonetop-group-fight-stat">
					<strong>Damage</strong>
					<a class="rollable stonetop-follower-damage-roll stonetop-group-fight-dmg-roll"
					   data-roll="d6"
					   data-follower-type="crew"
					   data-follower-name="{{#if name}}{{name}}{{else}}crew{{/if}}"
					   data-follower-pronoun="they"
					   data-damage-form="">
						<i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i>
					</a>
					<span class="stonetop-group-fight-dmg-label">d6</span>
				</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-group-fight-outnumber-row">
				<span class="stonetop-group-fight-outnumber-label">Outnumber:</span>
				<input class="stonetop-outnumber-yours" type="number" min="1"
				       value="{{#if individuals.length}}{{individuals.length}}{{else}}1{{/if}}">
				<span class="stonetop-outnumber-vs">vs</span>
				<input class="stonetop-outnumber-theirs" type="number" min="1" value="1">
				<span class="stonetop-outnumber-result"></span>
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-group-fight-roll-row">
				<button type="button" class="stonetop-group-fight-roll" data-stat="str">
					<i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i> Clash (STR)
				</button>
				<button type="button" class="stonetop-group-fight-roll" data-stat="dex">
					<i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i> Let Fly (DEX)
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
	{{/with}}
	{{/if}}

	{{!-- ── Initiates of Danu (Blessed) ───────────────────────── --}}
	{{#if stonetop.followers.initiates.length}}
	{{#each stonetop.followers.initiates}}
	<div class="stonetop-follower-card stonetop-follower-card--initiate">
		<div class="stonetop-follower-header">
			<div class="stonetop-follower-title">
				<span class="stonetop-follower-name">{{label}}{{#if pronoun}} <span class="stonetop-follower-pronoun">({{pronoun}})</span>{{/if}}</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-type">initiate of Danu</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-stats">
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat">
					<strong>HP</strong>
					<span class="stonetop-follower-hp-track">
						<input class="stonetop-follower-hp-input" type="number"
						       data-follower="initiate" data-slug="{{slug}}"
						       value="{{hpCurrent}}" min="0" max="{{hpMax}}">
						<span class="stonetop-hp-sep">/</span>
						<span class="stonetop-hp-max">{{hpMax}}</span>
					</span>
				</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Armor</strong> {{armor}}</span>
				<span class="stonetop-follower-stat"><strong>Damage</strong> {{#if damageRoll}}<a class="rollable stonetop-follower-damage-roll" data-roll="{{damageRoll}}" data-follower-type="initiate" data-follower-name="{{label}}" data-follower-pronoun="{{pronoun}}" data-damage-form="{{damageForm}}"><i class="fas fa-dice-d6"></i></a>{{/if}} {{damage}}</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{#if tags.length}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Tags</span>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-tags">
				{{#each tags}}<span class="stonetop-follower-tag">{{this}}</span>{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if choiceDetails.length}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Details</span>
			<div class="stonetop-follower-tags">
				{{#each choiceDetails}}<span class="stonetop-follower-tag stonetop-follower-tag--detail">{{this}}</span>{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if instinct}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Instinct</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{instinct}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		{{#if cost}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Cost</span>
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-value">{{cost}}</span>
		</div>
		{{/if}}
		<div class="stonetop-follower-row stonetop-follower-loyalty-row">
			<span class="stonetop-follower-row-label">Loyalty</span>
			<div class="stonetop-loyalty-pips">
				{{#each loyalty}}
				{{#if @root.stonetop.editMode}}
				<button type="button"
				        class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-initiate-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"
				        data-slug="{{slug}}" data-index="{{index}}"></button>
				{{else}}
				<span class="stonetop-loyalty-pip stonetop-initiate-loyalty-pip{{#if filled}} is-filled{{/if}}"></span>
				{{/if}}
				{{/each}}
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	{{/each}}

	{{/if}}

	{{!-- Follower special moves shared across all followers --}}
	<div class="stonetop-follower-card stonetop-follower-card--rules">
		<div class="stonetop-follower-rules-header">
			<h3 class="stonetop-follower-rules-title">Follower Special Moves</h3>
		</div>
		<div class="stonetop-follower-section stonetop-follower-rules">
			<details class="stonetop-follower-rule">
				<summary>Order Followers</summary>
				<p>When you <strong><em>direct your follower to do something that would trigger a player move</em></strong>, and they do it, they trigger the move. If the move involves rolling, you roll for them. Instead of rolling +STAT, roll and:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>If they have at least one appropriate tag or move, add +1, or +2 if they're also <em>exceptional</em></li>
					<li>If they have no relevant tag or move, add +0</li>
					<li>If any of their tags would get in the way, roll with disadvantage</li>
				</ul>
				<p>When a <strong><em>follower is without orders or they act on their own initiative</em></strong>, the GM says what they do and decides how it goes.</p>
			</details>
			<details class="stonetop-follower-rule">
				<summary>Strengthen Your Bond</summary>
				<p>When you <strong><em>pay your follower's cost and haven't done so recently</em></strong>, they hold +1 Loyalty (max 3).</p>
				<p>Spend your follower's Loyalty 1-for-1 to have them:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Overcome their fear to do as you say</li>
					<li>Resist acting on their instinct/tags/traits</li>
					<li>Do something they don't want to do (as long as it's not abhorrent or suicidal)</li>
				</ul>
			</details>
			<details class="stonetop-follower-rule">
				<summary>Loyal to the End</summary>
				<p>When <strong><em>one of your followers would die</em></strong>, you can spend 1 of their Loyalty to have them survive (out of the action, but alive). If you let them go, mark XP.</p>
			</details>
			<details class="stonetop-follower-rule">
				<summary>Followers in Fights</summary>
				<p>When a <strong><em>follower Aids you to Defend</em></strong>, you can spend 1 Readiness to have the follower suffer the damage/effects of an attack, or to have the follower draw all attention from your ward to itself.</p>
				<p>When a <strong><em>group of followers fights another group</em></strong>, roll a single Clash or Let Fly once for the whole group. Each side has HP and Armor and deals damage as one individual. Lost HP represents casualties proportionate to the group's original HP.</p>
				<p>If one side <strong><em>outnumbers the other</em></strong>, that side gets +1 Armor and +1 damage for each multiplier past the first (e.g. 3:1 gives +2 damage and +2 Armor).</p>
			</details>
		</div>
	</div>

</div>
</div>
